requirement: "data-text=" 2.4.3. Software "> 2.4.3. Software Watch device implementations: [3/W-0-1] MUST declare the feature android.hardware.type.watch. [3/W-0-2] MUST support uiMode = UI_MODE_TYPE_WATCH. [3.2.3.1/W-0-1] MUST preload one or more applications or service components with an intent handler, for all the public intent filter patterns defined by the following application intents listed <a href="https://developer.android.com/about/versions/11/reference/common-intents-30">here.
